# User Stories:

As a user:
1. I want to do a quiz and get a pet that matches my personality.
2. I want to be able to view a page with the details of my pet including name, bio (and stats - stretch)
3. I want to be able to change the name and bio of my pet.
4. I want to be able to register as a user so it saves my pet.

Stretch:
5. I want to be able to see a list of all users and their leaderboard score.
6. I want to be able to search users.
7. I want to be able to join a 'guild' - Team's Red/Yellow/Green and Blue, with its own chatroom.
8. I want to be able to select my pets class (which effects their stats).
9. I want to be able to train to upgrade my pets stats.
10. I want to be able to chat with other players regardless of team.
11. I want to see a leadboarder score for teams.
